<p id="id02345">Scott Mason picked up the phone on the first ring.</p>

<p id="id02346">"Scott Mason," he said without thinking.</p>

<p id="id02347">"Mr.  Mason?  This is Captain Kirk."  The voice was serious,  but
did  not resonate as did the distinctive voice that  belonged  to
