<p id="id02348">"Live long and prosper."  Mason replied in an emotionless voice.</p>

<p id="id02349">"I need to talk to you,"  the voice came right back.</p>

<p id="id02350">"So  talk."  Scott was used to anonymous callers so he  kept  the
