<p id="id02398">Hello.</p>

<p id="id02399">The computer screen paused briefly then came alive again.</p>

<h5 id="id02400">ARE YOU SCOTT MASON?</h5>

<p id="id02401">Scott entered 'Yes'.</p>

<h5 id="id02402">THIS IS KIRK</h5>

<p id="id02403">Scott wondered what the proper answer was to a non-question by  a
