<p id="id02404">Hello.   Again.</p>

<h5 id="id02405">IS THIS YOUR FIRST TIME?</h5>

<p id="id02406">What a question! Scott answered quickly.</p>

<p id="id02407">Please be gentle.</p>

<h5 id="id02408">NO . . .AT CHATTING ON COMPUTER . . .</h5>

<p id="id02409">I call the computer at work.  First time with a stranger.  Is  it
