<h5 id="id02413">IS THIS REALLY SCOTT MASON?</h5>

<p id="id02414">Yes.</p>

<h5 id="id02415">PROVE IT.</h5>

<p id="id02416">Kirk, or whoever this was, was comfortable with anonymity,  obvi-
ously.  And paranoid. Sure, play the game.</p>

<p id="id02417">You screwed up the NASA launch.</p>

