<p id="id02425">Sure, I think.</p>

<h5 id="id02426">NO  NO  NO . . .HACKERS.  WE'RE BASICALLY A GOOD  LOT  WHO  ENJOY
COMPUTERS FOR COMPUTERS SAKE.</h5>

<p id="id02427">That's what I've been saying</p>

<h5 id="id02428">REALLY.  HEY, DO YOU KNOW WHAT A HACKER REALLY IS?</h5>

<p id="id02429">A  guy who pokes his nose around where it's not wanted.  Like  in<br/>

NASA computers.<br/>
</p>

<h5 id="id02430">YEAH,  THAT'S WHAT THE PRESS SAYS AND SO THAT'S WHAT THE  COUNTRY
