<p id="id03437">Situated by the Danube of Strauss fame, Vienna, Austria is an odd
mixture  of the old, the very old and nouveau European high tech.
Downtown  Vienna is small, a semi-circle  of cobblestone  streets
and brash illuminated billboards at every juncture.</p>

<p id="id03438">Templer  contacted Alex through intermediaries stationed  in  Zu-
