whole bunch of white shirts in black hats, and Troubleaux . . ."</p>

<p id="id04733">"Troubleaux did you say?"</p>

<p id="id04734">"Yeah, that's what it says here . . ."</p>

<p id="id04735">"If he's there, then it becomes my concern, too."</p>

<p id="id04736">"Good,  glad you thought of it," joked Tyrone.  "If you catch  an
early  flight,  you  could be in D.C. by noon."   He  was  right,
thought  Scott.  The time difference works in your favor in  that
