<p id="id05521">Tyrone  pulled  the  first page from the printer  before  it  was
finished  and read to himself.  He scanned it quickly  until  one
item  grabbed  his attention. His eyes widened.  "Boy,  when  you
pick 'em, you pick 'em."  Tyrone whistled.</p>

<p id="id05522">"What, what?" Scott strained to see the printout, but Tyrone held
it away.</p>

<p id="id05523">"It's no wonder he calls himself Spook," Tyrone said to no one in
particular.  "He's ex-NSA."  He ripped off the final page of  the
printout  and called Scott to follow him, cursorily thanking  the
