right . . .shit . . .Delete . . . OK, that's it."</p>

<p id="id05535">"What are you doing?" asked Scott.</p>

<p id="id05536">"Just want to see if your boy really was in Europe with you."</p>

<p id="id05537">"You don't believe me!" shouted Scott.</p>

<p id="id05538">"No,  I believe you.  But I need some proof, dig?"  Tyrone  said.<br/>

"If he's up to something we need to find out what, step by  step.<br/>

You should know that."<br/>
</p>

<p id="id05539">"Yeah,  I do," Scott resigned.  "It's just that I'm not  normally
the one being questioned. Know what I mean?"</p>

<p id="id05540">"Our  training is more  . . .well, it's a moot point  now.   Your
Mr. Foster flew to Amsterdam and then back to Washington the next
day.  I believe I have some legwork ahead of me.  I would like to
learn a little more about Mr. Miles Foster."</p>

<p id="id05541">Scott  talked Tyrone into giving him a copy of one of the  images
of  Miles  aka  Spook.  He was hoping that Kirk  would  call  him
tonight.   In any case, Scott needed to buy an image  scanner  if
