<p id="id05542">At  midnight,  on the button, Scott's computer  beeped.   It  was<br/>

Kirk.<br/>
</p>

<h5 id="id05543">WTFO</h5>

<p id="id05544">You got my message.</p>

<h5 id="id05545">SUBTLETY IS NOT YOUR STRONG POINT</h5>

<p id="id05546">I didn't want to miss.</p>

