<p id="id06880">The  NSA is further recommending federal legislation to  mitigate
the  effects of future computer attacks.  They propose that  com-
puter security be required by law.</p>

<p id="id06881">"We  feel that it would be prudent to ask the private  sector  to
comply  with  minimum security levels. The C2 level  is  easy  to
reach, and will deter all but the most dedicated assaults.  It is
